Tried this chocolaty and delicious Nutella Oreo mix in our Personalized Can Glass Tumbler and it was finished within minutes 😍

Quick Recipe:
1. Add Nutella to a glass tumbler.
2. Add some Oreos and crush them.
3. Pour milk into the mixture.
4. In a self-stirring mug, add coffee and water.
5. Blend it well.
6. Pour the coffee mixture into the tumbler.
7. Mix everything thoroughly — and voilà, your drink is ready!
